ActCanadian Commercial Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of JULIAN J. OVENS of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Commercial Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Daniela Bassan, whose term has expired.
